  <description>
    <p>An English language dictionary applet, perfect for quick access searching for words and definitions, or cycling through some random words to further enrich your knowledge of the English language.</p>
    <p>Contains all English words, including profanity and offensive terms. The random function could also show any of these.</p>
    <p>Based on the open source Wordset Dictionary. Please visit the repository for details on submitting additions and corrections.</p>
  </description>
